Package: tornadoexposure
Type: Package
Title: Explore and Map ZCTA-Level Tornado Exposures in the United States
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Hailey Hansen
Maintainer: <hailhan@uchicago.edu>
Description: This package contains data and functions to allow users to explore
    and map ZCTA-level tornado exposures in the United States from 1954-2025.
    Data comes from the NOAA Severe Weather Database and the Census Bureau. 
    Tornados of magnitude EF 3 and greater are included in the dataset.
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/hailhan/tornadoexposure
BugReports: https://github.com/hailhan/tornadoexposure/issues
Imports:
  ggplot2,
  sf,
  tigris
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
